<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:#66cc00"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>3. Câu hỏi:</strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>- Cấu trúc</strong></span></span></span></p>

